track_notes:
Aufstieg von Richtung Mürli mit Traversierung zu  Gras-Band in linker Berghälfte (linker Bergabschnitt)
Abstieg via Normal-Route (West-Rinne)

This is quite a common route to the summit and there are official, well-visible hiking paths all along the way. Two comments to keep in mind, however:

1) The parking spaces at the Wägitalersee are found along the road and they are few and far between. Additionally, the lake is popular among fishermen. Come early! Especially on the weekends, otherwise, you will not find any parking.

2) At 47.08521, 8.95816, I decided to take a shortcut up to the summit. Note that this is decidedly *not* an official route - it leads over wild and rough terrain and is quite steep. Only follow this track if you know what you are doing and are in a hurry - otherwise, stick to the official route.

If you are ambitious, it is possible to do HB/GL-033, HB/GL-031 and HB/SZ-034 on a single day. Please refer to the tracks on those summits to see the routes I took there.
